(g) the Secretary General of the Ministry responsible for
information, or his representative;
(h) the Attorney General of Malaysia, or his representative;
(i) the Inspector General of Police, or his representative;
(j) the Director-General of Immigration, or his representative;
(k) the Director-General of Customs, or his representative;
(l) the Director-General of Malaysian Maritime Enforcement,
or his representative;
(la) the Director-General of the Department of Women’s
Development, or his representative;
(lb) the Director-General of Social Welfare Department, or his
representative;
(lc) the Director-General of Labour, Department of Labour of
Peninsular Malaysia, or his representative;
(ld) Director of Labour, Department of Labour Sabah, or his
representative;
(le) Director of Labour, Department of Labour Sarawak, or his
representative;
(m) a representative of the following Ministries:
(i) the Ministry responsible for internal security;
(ii) the Ministry responsible for defence;
(iii) the Ministry responsible for medical and health
service;
(iv) the Ministry responsible for development of youth
and sports;
